Title: BISSELL Little Green® Portable Carpet Cleaner 3369
Description: Not every pet mess calls for a full-size carpet cleaning machine. Use BISSELL® Little Green® portable upholstery and carpet cleaner to spray, scrub and lift away those smaller messes, like dirt and stains, from all types of surfaces. It has powerful suction to easily remove dirty paw prints from carpets and stairs, plus it works on car interiors, too! Little Green® portable deep cleaner is lightweight, so you can use it almost anywhere. And this machine doesn’t just clean up after pets, it helps save them! BISSELL proudly supports BISSELL Pet Foundation® and its mission to help save homeless pets. When you buy a BISSELL® product, you help save pets, too. We’re proud to design products that help make pet messes, odors and pet homelessness disappear.

Title: Dyson V7 Advanced Cordless Vacuum Cleaner | Silver | New
Description:
The Dyson V7 Advanced cordless vacuum cleaner is engineered with the power, versatility and run time to clean your whole home. Dyson’s de-tangling Motorbar™ cleaner head deep cleans carpets and hard floors with hair removal vanes that clear long hair and pet hair from the brush bar. The Dyson V7 has advanced, whole-machine filtration that captures pet allergens and fine dust, expelling cleaner air. Thanks to the cordless format, it also transforms into a handheld vacuum with one click so you can clean up high, down low and everywhere in-between. Comes with a 2-year warranty and lifetime Dyson support.
¹Actual run time will vary based on power mode and/or attachments used. ²In Max mode. All other modes achieve at least 99.97% filtration. Washable filter can be reused for the lifetime of the machine, reducing waste.


In the box: Dyson V7 Advanced Cordless Vacuum Cleaner, Motorbar cleaner head, Combination Tool, Mini Soft Dusting Brush, Charger.

Title: Dyson V12 Detect Slim Cordless Vacuum Cleaner | Nickel | New
Description:
The Dyson V12 Detect Slim is Dyson's lightest intelligent cordless vacuum. It's engineered with the power, intelligence, versatility, and run time to deep clean your whole home in a lightweight, compact format. Dyson illumination reveals invisible dust on hard floors. The Dyson V12 Detect Slim intelligently optimizes power and run time based on the debris picked up, reporting it all on the LCD screen.³ The LCD screen also displays the run time countdown, power modes, and maintenance alerts. Dyson's de-tangling Motorbar™ cleaner head deep cleans carpets and hard floors without tangles. Its versatile cordless format transforms into a handheld vacuum with one click so you can clean up high, down low, and everywhere in between. Title: BISSELL PowerForce Helix Bagless Upright Vacuum 3313
Description: BISSELL® PowerForce® Helix® bagless upright vacuum (new and improved version of model 2191) is a lightweight and powerful vacuum that removes embedded dirt and hair from your home and offers long-lasting performance. The large-capacity dirt tank holds more, expanding your opportunity for room-to-room cleaning. Onboard tools work for cleaning above floors, and the edge-to-edge floor cleaning is great for hard-to-reach areas like baseboards and around furniture. BISSELL® PowerForce® Helix® bagless upright vacuum is a go-to for keeping your home tidy. It offers a Helix® dirt separation system that helps keep your washable filters newer for a longer time. The trusted bagless upright vacuum also has extended suction power and cleaning performance. Five height settings make it easy to clean almost any surface. Tackle what the kids track in on the living room carpet, then move directly to picking up those crumbs from kitchen tile. It goes everywhere you need it. There is a 23 foot power cord. BISSELL proudly supports BISSELL Pet Foundation® and its mission to help save homeless pets. When you buy a BISSELL® product, you help save pets, too. We’re proud to design products that help make pet messes, odors and pet homelessness disappear.

Title: Dyson Big Ball Turbinehead Canister Vacuum | Yellow/Iron | New
Description:
The Dyson Big Ball Turbinehead has powerful Dyson suction to remove hair and dirt from every floor type. Self-righting technology Dyson Big Ball canister vacuums are monostatic: they have a single stable resting point. Dyson engineers made this possible using a complex configuration of the vacuum’s components. By assembling them in a spherical array, with the heaviest components near the floor, we created a curved body with a low center of gravity. This means that whenever the vacuum is displaced from its resting position, gravitational force will automatically return it. Or more simply, when it’s knocked over, it gets back up. Dyson Big Ball canister vacuums feature a new bin emptying mechanism so you can hygienically drive out trapped dust and debris with just the push of a button. With advanced whole-machine filtration and 4 additional tools for versatile tasks, the Turbinehead tool automatically raises and lowers to seal in suction across carpets, rugs, and hard floors. Articulated handle for easy, versatile cleaning the wand’s handle rotates in three directions, allowing 360° articulation for greater control.

In the box: Quick-release articulating hard floor tool, Quick-release combination tool, Stair tool, Tangle-free Turbine head.
